{"tid":2462603,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【私樓落成量】中小型單位空置率升至4% 創近10年新高","createTime":"2021-03-26T05:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T05:58:08.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5865d5f7785476f5816aa93fb858926d0061b18a","tid":2462603,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:58:08.000Z","msg":"【私樓落成量】中小型單位空置率升至4% 創近10年新高<br />\n12:49 2021/03/26<br />\n<br />\n&quot;去年私人住宅空置率上升至4.3%，按年升0.6個百分點，其中小型單位更屬「重災區」，多達4.5萬個單位置，空置率罕有升達4%，創近10年新高，再加上新樓落成急增，今年私樓租金將會繼續面臨下調壓力......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2917428/%E3%80%90%E7%A7%81%E6%A8%93%E8%90%BD%E6%88%90%E9%87%8F%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E5%9E%8B%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E7%8E%87%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B34%25%20%20%E5%89%B5%E8%BF%9110%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2917428%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25A7%2581%25E6%25A8%2593%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2587%258F%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%259E%258B%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E7%258E%2587%25E5%258D%2587%25E8%2587%25B34%2525%2520%2520%25E5%2589%25B5%25E8%25BF%259110%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Gr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=b88415ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2917428/%E3%80%90%E7%A7%81%E6%A8%93%E8%90%BD%E6%88%90%E9%87%8F%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E5%9E%8B%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E7%8E%87%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B34%25%20%20%E5%89%B5%E8%BF%9110%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98?mtc=60037</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>樓淡會話因為私樓租金將會繼續面臨下調壓力，所以決定繼續租樓日日(俾業主)賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"}]}